## Project Layout

```
_quarto.yml         # Documentation configuration
Makefile            # Build targets (docs, preview, test-contracts, clean)
notebooks/
    example.py      # Jupytext percent-format notebook examples
    contracts/      # ATDD contract notebooks (.py source of truth)
    archive/        # Frozen archived notebooks (.ipynb with outputs)
docs/
    index.qmd       # Documentation homepage
    CHANGELOG.md    # Project changelog
    reference/      # Auto-generated API docs (quartodoc)
src/
    {{project_name}}/  # Python package source
```
